patthana17.9:0.2_0: (This should be expanded as in the teachings.)
patthana17.9:1.1_0: it doesn’t give rise to the teaching from material skillful qualities. And I don’t give rise to a cause or condition.
patthana17.9:2.1_0: Hateness arises dependent on the skillful and unskillful is not something for the sake of worldly gain.
patthana17.9:3.1_0: not declared: ‘This is a cause of schism in the teaching.’
